#: ../../source/user_guide/linear_solvers.rst:158
#: 70addf5649274257b1d25afc150d9110
msgid ""
"When ``b`` has shape ``[n_dof, n_batch]``, ``torch-sla`` automatically "
"amortizes the factorization across the batch — one factor pass, "
"``n_batch`` back-substitutions — instead of running an iterative solver "
"independently per column. This is the workhorse of the "
":mod:`tensormesh.dataset` ML workflow."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/user_guide/linear_solvers.rst:169
#: e2011ec7ad2243149c7024634ba8f5cc
